spanGrp.span: In the old days when I was a daughter
When I grew I went to the meeting of the youths and I was made some clothes with beads.
aa gaahis heed geaeahondanaan amiit geaeafk aa geaeanap aqoadeeny baa gileeng
àà gááhís hééd gɛ́ɛ́hòndànáán àmíít gɛ́ɛ́fk àà gɛ́ɛ́nàp àqɔ̀dèèɲ báá gílééŋg
Nilipokua nikaenda unyagoni hatimaye nikashonewa ngozi yangu yenye ushanga.
I was sewn a special gourd for cosmetics.
Nikashonewa kibuyu maalum kwa ajili ya vipodozi.
It had beads sewn around it
This animal skin I would wear when we went to ngoma.
Ngozi hiyo huwa ninaivaa siku tukienda ngoma.
When I arrive at the ngoma I choose the person I will dance with.
Nikifika kwenye ngoma namwanzishia nitakayecheza naye .
I choose a boy with the same age as me.
I am the same age as him.
On the day I go to get married.
I wake up and go to my home.
I went to to be with him and another day...
nitaenda kuwa naye na siku nyingine
If there is another girl from our family who is going to be married, she will take the gourd with her to her new family.
aa gwand digahany giqamaqaan aa qoat qeend niiny qoat qaareaeadany
àà gwánd dígáháɲ gìqàmàqáán àà qɔ́t qéènd nííɲ qɔ́t qáàrɛ̀ɛ̀dàɲ
Kama kuna binti wa kwetu mwingine atakayeenda kuolewa atakuja kukichukua ili aolewe nacho na atakipeleka nyumbani kwake.
This is how it was, this is where we came from.
aha gwasiin aha aseaeas qay ed sing'eaeadeaeawi
àhá gwásììn àhá ásɛ́ɛ́s qáj éd síŋɛ́ɛ̀dɛ̀ɛ̀wì
Na ndivyo ilivyo, sisi ndiko tulikotokea zamani.
For us Asimjeeg, this is our work.
Kwa sisi Waasmjega kazi yetu ndiyo hiyo.
na ndugu yako wa kiume akioa....
You will go to bring the wife home.
Even she will have her own gourd.
aa niiny seen gigwandaw gideshtaydany aa gwandaw aqoadany
àà nííɲ séèn gìgwàndàw gìdéʃtájdáɲ áà gwándáw áqɔ́dàɲ
Hata yeye naye atakuwa na kibuyu chake na ngozi yake.
And she will be sent to be shown cows and after the celebration...
aha gijeaeayat jeed dugw aa geaeahim dugw hay amwaqang'at nyangiidanyi
àhà gídʒɛ́ɛ́ját dʒééd dúgw àà gɛ́ɛ́hím dùgw hàj àmwáqàŋàt ɲàŋgíídáɲì
na atapelekwa na kuonyeshwa ng'ombe na siku sherehe ikipita
She is given her cows and then she starts to go to her home and begin work with her husband.
geaeataw aha dugwasch aa gabiis gaw qareaeadany gwasin gadiyedany ha gwargweaeadany
gɛ̀ɛ̀táw áhá dúgwástʃ áá gábíís gàw qárɛ́ɛ́dàɲ gwàsín gàdíjédáɲ há gwàrgwɛ́ɛ́dàɲ
Anapewa ng'ombe zake na anaanza kwenda nyumbani kwake afanye kazi na mume wake.
